title: Enjoyable quirky film
review:
Really good movie, really enjoyable. My partner and I came across the trailer online few days ago! Really eye catching and enjoying so we ordered the dvd. We both really enjoyed it, both completely hooked to the movie time
Flew by! Really catchy ending too! Look forward to Seeing what the guys release next well done guys good job done! Defo a must watch

title: Irish action fun
review: I found this a few days ago on Sky and as an action movie fan thought i'd give it a go. Actually ended up really enjoying it, it was cheesy fun, with some good action and fights, and some enjoyable characters. Worth a few hours of your time for some evening entertainment!

title: Great watch
review: Watched this film with my partner last night, we both really enjoyed it, so different to anything we have seen before! Great twist in the storyline too! Well done team
